sentences: Olga Von Till (March 27, 1897 – February 6, 1996) was an American classical pianist and piano teacher.
Till was born in the borough of Brooklyn, New York in 1897.
Von Till died on February 6, 1996 and is buried in Van Liew Cemetery in North Brunswick, New Jersey.
While living in Hungary, Von Till met Hugó Kormos and married him in 1919.
